   "source": [
    "# Chess RL with Curriculum Learning vs Stockfish\n",
    "\n",
    "**Strategy: Curriculum Learning**\n",
    "- Start with weak Stockfish (depth 1)\n",
    "- NN learns to beat it\n",
    "- Auto-increase difficulty when win rate > 60%\n",
    "- Progress: depth 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 6 → 8 → 12+\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture: Original Lc0 with MCTS**\n",
    "- 112-plane board encoding\n",
    "- ResNet trunk\n",
    "- Policy + Value + WDL heads\n",
    "- Monte Carlo Tree Search for move selection\n"
   ]
  },
